videos.description: Georges Niang and Buddy Hield have nothing but praise for each other after Oklahoma State fends off Iowa State. Hield won the scoring battle, with 39 points to Niang's 31 points.
videos.headline: Niang and Hield: 'Tonight was special'

videos.description: Miles Simon and Jon Sciambi break down Oklahoma's win against Iowa State with Buddy Hield's 39-point performance
videos.headline: Oklahoma shuts down Iowa State

videos.description: Scott Van Pelt thought it was really cool that Buddy Hield and Georges Niang interviewed together after competing. Hield is not concerned with being the best player in the country, rather he just wants Oklahoma to win.
